data.title: Microsoft Corporation Black Book
data.meta_description: Microsoft Corporation Black Book - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Microsoft Corporation is a multinational technology company headquartered in Redmond, Washington. It develops, manufactures, licenses, and supports software, services, devices, and solutions. Bill Gates and Paul Allen founded Microsoft in 1975. Some of Microsoft's most popular products include the Windows operating system, Microsoft Office, Xbox, and Bing. Throughout its history, Microsoft has faced antitrust lawsuits and accusations of anti-competitive behavior. The company continues to be a leader in the technology industry with a focus on cloud computing and artificial intelligence.
